title: [Teorainn Valley, Lake Tanai]
description: The lake glistens in the moonlight.  To the east, barely visible through a tall, thick tangle of brambles, is some sort of wooden structure suspended in the branches of a tall oak tree.  To the south the terrain rises sharply, becoming a rocky escarpment dotted with thanot shrubs.
